Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:03.04,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)\c&HC3D0FA&\3c&H707DA1&}纵使待到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:05.14,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使待到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.31,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}云雾也不会散去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:09.71,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使太阳升起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:12.34,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}也无法看见你
