Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.55,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}享受现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.79,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}充满谜团的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}无法解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:28.59,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}满是罪孽的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:31.06,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}每天的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:31.76,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}请给予我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:34.07,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那已知的今天与未知的明天的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:36.30,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}就此启程去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:38.50,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那声音
